s="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path fill="currentColor" d="M224 256A128 128 0 1 0 224 0a128 128 0 1 0 0 256zm-45.7 48C79.8 304 0 383.8 0 482.3C0 498.7 13.3 512 29.7 512l388.6 0c16.4 0 29.7-13.3 29.7-29.7C448 383.8 368.2 304 269.7 304l-91.4 0z"></path></svg>Agent Builder</a></div></aside></div><div class="main-content"><div class="mobile-header"><img alt="Ultimo Bots Logo" width="140" height="57" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="ultimo-bots-mobile-logo" style="color:transparent" srcset="/_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-purple.webp&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-purple.webp&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x" src="./wordpress_files/ultimo-bots-purple.jpeg"><button class="hamburger" aria-label="Toggle Sidebar">☰</button></div><section class="wixSection" id="wix"><div class="wixHero"><div class="wixWrap"><div class="wixHeroLeft"><h1 class="wixHeroTitle">The highest-rated AI chatbot for WordPress websites</h1><p class="wixHeroSub">Install the Ultimo Bots plugin from the WordPress Plugin Directory and get a fully trained chatbot live on your site in 2 minutes.</p><div class="wixHeroActions"><a class="wixCtaPrimary" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/ultimo-bots" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Install on WordPress</a><span class="wixHeroNote">2-minute plugin setup</span></div></div><div class="wixHeroRight"><div class="wixHeroMedia"><video class="wixHeroVideo" autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" preload="metadata"></video><button class="wixProgressBtn" aria-label="Play video"><span class="wixProgressBg"></span><svg class="wixProgressRing" viewBox="0 0 44 44"><circle class="wixRingTrack" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="4" fill="none"></circle><circle class="wixRingProgress" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="4" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="113.09733552923255" stroke-dashoffset="110.77145897443066"></circle></svg><span class="wixIconPlay"></span></button></div></div></div></div><div class="wixHighlights"><div class="wixWrap"><div class="wixPill">Why it stands out on WordPress</div><div class="wixHeader"><h2 class="wixTitle">Built for WordPress, not just embedded into it</h2><p class="wixSub">Ultimo Bots is designed around the WordPress ecosystem, so setup, training, and management feel native and effortless inside your admin dashboard.</p></div><div class="wixHighlightGrid"><article class="wixCard"><div class="wixMedia"><img alt="Chatbot trained on your WordPress content" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="wixImg" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 380px" srcset="/_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-1.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="./wordpress_files/ultimo-bots-highlights-1.jpeg" style="position: absolute; height: 100%; width: 100%; inset: 0px; color: transparent;"></div><h3 class="wixCardTitle">Understands your WordPress site</h3><p class="wixCardText">Train the chatbot on your WordPress pages, blog, store, and FAQs to answer like a real team member.</p></article><article class="wixCard"><div class="wixMedia"><img alt="Fast WordPress plugin integration" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="wixImg" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 380px" srcset="/_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-2.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="./wordpress_files/ultimo-bots-highlights-2.jpeg" style="position: absolute; height: 100%; width: 100%; inset: 0px; color: transparent;"></div><h3 class="wixCardTitle">Native WordPress plugin installation</h3><p class="wixCardText">Install the plugin directly from the WordPress Plugin Directory with a guided flow that takes less than two minutes.</p></article><article class="wixCard"><div class="wixMedia"><img alt="Swiss hosting and privacy for WordPress" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="wixImg" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 380px" srcset="/_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fultimo-bots-highlights-3.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="./wordpress_files/ultimo-bots-highlights-3.jpeg" style="position: absolute; height: 100%; width: 100%; inset: 0px; color: transparent;"></div><h3 class="wixCardTitle">Secure and privacy-focused</h3><p class="wixCardText">Swiss hosting, GDPR compliance, and transparent controls over what the chatbot can access from your WordPress site.</p></article></div></div></div><div class="wixMarket"><div class="wixWrap"><div class="wixMarketLayout"><div class="wixMarketLeft"><h2 class="wixTitle">Top-rated AI chatbot plugin for WordPress</h2><p class="wixMarketSub">Among all chatbot plugins on WordPress, Ultimo Bots is rated at the top, with users praising its accuracy, ease of use, and support.</p><ul class="wixMarketList"><li>Best-rated AI chatbot plugin across popular WordPress options</li><li>Loved by agencies, e-commerce stores, and service businesses on WordPress</li><li>Continuously improved with real feedback from WordPress users</li></ul><div class="wixBottomCtaRow"><a class="wixCtaPrimary" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/ultimo-bots" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View in WordPress Plugin Directory</a></div></div><div class="wixHeroRight"><div class="wixMarketMedia"><img alt="Ultimo Bots plugin listing for WordPress" loading="lazy" width="2233" height="1258" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="wixMarketImg" srcset="/_next/image?url=%2Fwordpress-blog%2Fwordpress_plugin_overview.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" src="./wordpress_files/wordpress_plugin_overview.jpeg" style="color: transparent;"><div class="wixMarketOverlay"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wixHow"><div class="wixWrap"><div class="wixPill">How it works</div><div class="wixHeader"><h2 class="wixTitle">From plugin install to live chatbot in 2 minutes</h2><p class="wixSub">A simple, guided flow inside your WordPress admin takes care of everything for you. No code, no scripts, no technical setup.</p></div><div class="wixLayout"><div class="wixLeft"><ul class="wixList" role="tablist" aria-orientation="vertical"><li class="wixItem wixActive"><button role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="wix-how-panel-1" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixNum">01.</span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">Add the WordPress plugin</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixDescOpen">Install the Ultimo Bots plugin from the WordPress Plugin Directory in a few clicks.</span></span></button></li><li class="wixItem "><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="wix-how-panel-2" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixNum">02.</span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">Connect your website content</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixDescClosed">Let the chatbot learn from your WordPress pages, FAQs, and documents.</span></span></button></li><li class="wixItem "><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="wix-how-panel-3" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixNum">03.</span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">Go live in 2 minutes</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixDescClosed">Publish and have a fully trained chatbot on your WordPress site.</span></span></button></li><li class="wixItem "><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="wix-how-panel-4" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixNum">04.</span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">Handle complex questions</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixDescClosed">Let the chatbot respond or route conversations to your team directly from your WordPress site.</span></span></button></li><li class="wixItem "><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="wix-how-panel-5" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixNum">05.</span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">Track performance</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixDescClosed">See what visitors ask, what converts, and where to improve inside your WordPress dashboard.</span></span></button></li></ul></div><div class="wixRight" id="wix-how-panel-1" role="tabpanel" aria-live="polite"><div class="wixScreen"><video class="wixVideo" poster="/how-it-works-1.webm" autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" preload="metadata"><source src="/how-it-works-1.webm" type="video/webm"></video><button class="wixProgressBtn" aria-label="Play video"><span class="wixProgressBg"></span><svg class="wixProgressRing" viewBox="0 0 44 44"><circle class="wixRingTrack" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="4" fill="none"></circle><circle class="wixRingProgress" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="4" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="113.09733552923255" stroke-dashoffset="69.18961928360844"></circle></svg><span class="wixIconPlay"></span></button></div></div></div><div class="wixBottomCtaRow"><a class="wixCtaPrimary" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/ultimo-bots" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Install Plugin</a></div></div></div><div class="wixBenefits"><div class="wixWrap"><div class="wixPill">What you get</div><div class="wixHeader"><h2 class="wixTitle">Your WordPress chatbot that feels like a real team member</h2><p class="wixSub">Ultimo Bots helps WordPress sites answer questions, qualify leads, and support customers around the clock.</p></div><div class="wixBenefitsLayout"><div class="wixStage"><video class="wixVideo" poster="/benefits-1.webm" autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" preload="metadata"></video><button class="wixProgressBtn" aria-label="Play video"><span class="wixProgressBg"></span><svg class="wixProgressRing" viewBox="0 0 44 44"><circle class="wixRingTrack" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="4" fill="none"></circle><circle class="wixRingProgress" cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="4" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="113.09733552923255" stroke-dashoffset="38.41871463237696"></circle></svg><span class="wixIconPlay"></span></button></div><div class="wixBenefitsRight"><ul class="wixList" role="tablist" aria-orientation="vertical"><li class="wixItem wixActive"><button role="tab" aria-selected="true" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixIcon" aria-hidden="true"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="user-check" class="svg-inline--fa fa-user-check " role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 640 512"><path fill="currentColor" d="M96 128a128 128 0 1 1 256 0A128 128 0 1 1 96 128zM0 482.3C0 383.8 79.8 304 178.3 304l91.4 0C368.2 304 448 383.8 448 482.3c0 16.4-13.3 29.7-29.7 29.7L29.7 512C13.3 512 0 498.7 0 482.3zM625 177L497 305c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-64-64c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9s24.6-9.4 33.9 0l47 47L591 143c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0s9.4 24.6 0 33.9z"></path></svg></span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">Best-rated WordPress chatbot</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixOpen">Top-rated AI chatbot plugin for WordPress websites across multiple industries.</span></span></button></li><li class="wixItem "><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixIcon" aria-hidden="true"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="bolt" class="svg-inline--fa fa-bolt " role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path fill="currentColor" d="M349.4 44.6c5.9-13.7 1.5-29.7-10.6-38.5s-28.6-8-39.9 1.8l-256 224c-10 8.8-13.6 22.9-8.9 35.3S50.7 288 64 288l111.5 0L98.6 467.4c-5.9 13.7-1.5 29.7 10.6 38.5s28.6 8 39.9-1.8l256-224c10-8.8 13.6-22.9 8.9-35.3s-16.6-20.7-30-20.7l-111.5 0L349.4 44.6z"></path></svg></span><span class="wixTexts"><span class="wixItemTitle">2-minute plugin setup</span><span class="wixItemDesc wixClosed">No code, no copy-paste, no scripts. Install the plugin, connect your content, and go live instantly.</span></span></button></li><li class="wixItem "><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" class="wixBtn"><span class="wixIcon" aria-hidden="true"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="comment-dots" class="svg-inline--fa fa-comment-dots " role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path fill="currentColor" d="M256 448c141.4 0 256-93.1 256-208S397.4 32 256 32S0 125.1 0 240c0 45.1 17.7 86.8 47.7 120.9c-1.9 24.5-11.4 46.3-21.4 62.9c-5.5 9.2-11.1 16.6-15.2 21.6c-2.1 2.5-3.7 4.4-4.9 5.7c-.6 .6-1 1.1-1.3 1.4l-.3 .3c0 0 0 0 0 0c0 0 0 0 0 0s0 0 0 0s0 0 0 0c-4.6 4.6-5.9 11.4-3.4 17.4c2.5 6 8.3 9.9 14.8 9.9c28.7 0 57.6-8.9 81.6-19.3c22.9-10 42.4-21.9 54.3-30.6c31.8 11.5 67 17.9 104.1 17.9zM128 208a32 32 0 1 1 0 64 32 32 0 1 1 0-64zm128 0a32 32 0 1 1 0 64 32 32 0 1 1 0-64zm96 32a32 32 0 1 1 64 0 32 32 0 1 1 -64 0z"></path></svg></span><span class="wixTexts"><spa